Create a modern, premium dark-themed SaaS website UI with a futuristic glassmorphism design.

Design Requirements:

• Theme:
- Dark navy/black gradient background (#060a12 to #080d18)
- Subtle glowing particles or grid floor perspective effect
- Smooth ambient lighting for depth

• Typography:
- Use Inter font
- Bold, clean headings with slight letter spacing
- Gradient text for headings (white to gray)

• Layout:
- Centered section with large heading: "Our Services"
- Subtitle below with muted gray color
- 3 responsive cards in a row (stack on mobile)

• Cards (Glassmorphism Style):
- Semi-transparent background (rgba white 0.03–0.06)
- Backdrop blur (20px)
- Soft border with low opacity white
- Rounded corners (16px–20px)
- Subtle hover animation (lift + glow + border highlight)

• Card Content:
Each card should contain:
- Minimal icon inside a rounded square (glass style)
- Title (e.g., Health Insurance, Life Insurance, Motor Insurance)
- Short description (muted text)

• Effects & Animations:
- Smooth fade-in on load
- Hover: translateY(-5px), border glow, soft shadow
- Background animated grid or perspective floor

• Buttons:
- Rounded pill buttons
- Glass style with blur and border
- Hover: brighter background + slight lift

• Navbar:
- Transparent or glass style navbar
- Logo on left
- Links: About, Services, Why Us, Testimonials
- CTA button: "Get Quote"

• Responsiveness:
- Fully responsive
- Cards stack vertically on mobile
- Proper spacing and padding

• Aesthetic:
- Clean, minimal, premium SaaS feel
- Inspired by modern fintech / insurance / AI startups
- Focus on depth, blur, and subtle motion

Tech (optional if needed):
- HTML + Tailwind / React + Tailwind / Next.js
- Use reusable components
- Keep code clean and production-ready
